<para>All state and lifecycle declarations live in <ref refid="ddc__core_8h" kindref="compound">ddc/ddc_core.h</ref>. This header exists so jm-managed <ref refid="ddc__ext__ddcr_8c" kindref="compound">ddc_ext_ddcr.c</ref> can include a component-specific path while still resolving against the shared <ref refid="ddc__core_8h_1aec244c9fe5060253d7d68356f5f03131" kindref="member">ddcr_state_t</ref> defined alongside <ref refid="ddc__core_8h_1a7e5d786dd8f49cb2f48bf5b0b8e6247e" kindref="member">ddc_state_t</ref>. </para>
